data.description: This splendid property encompasses 15 sprawling acres, featuring a 2,163 square-foot main residence boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Adjacent is a delightful 792 square-foot pool house, complete with a bedroom, full bath, and a well-appointed kitchen, perfectly complementing the saltwater pool for the ultimate retreat. Experience the best of both worlds—serene countryside living with all the comforts of an elegant home and poolside relaxation in the heart of the charming city of Vidalia. Welcome Home!
